reviews.name: Wintec 4GB DDR3 Laptop Memory Upgrade Kit 1333MHz with SODIMM Chip, Screw Driver, Anti-Static (ES) Strap & more
reviews.reviewText: I ordered a new computer and at the same time ordered a 4GB memory upgrade thinking I would be getting a new computer with 8GB of RAM. Uhhhh, NO! that is not the way it works. I got a computer with 4 GB of RAM and I got another 4 GB card in a separate box. Since there was only ONE memory slot, the 4GB upgrade was identical to the one already installed and I could not use the upgrade.
reviews.title: Don't Make MY Mistake
